[dl 
	[dt 
		"Bypass collision detection
	]dt
	[dd 
		"If you are 3 frames away from a hit, you can disable collision detection as long as you are constantly changing between the 3 characters (select button) until you are out of the range of enemy hitboxes.
		$LF
	]dd
